headline: JP Morgan Maintains Overweight on McDonald's, Raises Price Target to $325
summary: JP Morgan  analyst John Ivankoe   maintains McDonald's (NYSE:MCD) with a Overweight and raises the price target from $305 to $325.

headline: McDonald's India (W&S) Celebrates Protein Week, Encourages Everyday Protein Choices
summary: In the run-up to World Protein Day on 27th February, McDonald's India (West & South), owned and operated by Westlife Foodworld, is celebrating Protein Week, reinforcing its leadership in nutrition-led innovation. Making protein more accessible, affordable and customizable, Indian consumers can use the McDonald's app to explore these nutritious offerings and avail of protein burgers starting at just INR 69. Enhancing this convenience, consumers ordering via McDelivery can also enjoy free delivery
